    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a practical option for someone seeking dependable transportation without the premium price tag of a newer model. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including several visible scratches on the side panels and some minor fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is intact but displays some staining and light wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly maintained, though it may require some minor cosmetic attention to truly shine. It is a solid, functional vehicle that is ready for daily use.",
